        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">In general, there are there are two types of controls: open-loop control (feedforward), and closed-loop control (feedback). In many applications of practical relevance, the state vector x is very high-dimensional, even though input u and output y may be low-dimensional.</rdfs:comment>
