        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Empirical distribution of individuals that follow a specific medium and influencer at a given time by the sum of Dirac Delta distributions placed at the individuals’ opinions.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Empirical Distribution of Individuals</rdfs:label>
