        <definingFormulation rdf:datatype="https://mardi4nfdi.de/mathmoddb#LaTeX">$\frac{dc_{ES}}{dt}=k_{1}*c_{E}*c_{S}-k_{-1}*c_{ES}-k_{2}*c_{ES}+k_{-2}*c_{E}*c_{P}$</definingFormulation>
