        <definingFormulation rdf:datatype="https://mardi4nfdi.de/mathmoddb#LaTeX">$\frac{c_S}{v_0} = \frac{c_S (1 + \frac{c_I}{K_{iu}})}{V_{max,f}} + \frac{K_m (1 + \frac{c_I}{K_{ic}})}{V_{max,f}}$</definingFormulation>
