        <definingFormulation rdf:datatype="https://mardi4nfdi.de/mathmoddb#LaTeX">$\frac{dc_{P_2}}{dt} = k_{4} c_{EP_{1}P_{2}} - k_{-4} c_{EP_1} c_{P_2}$</definingFormulation>
