        <terms1:description xml:lang="en">quantum dynamics of an open system, i.e., a system that interacts with its environment</terms1:description>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Quantum dynamics of an open system, i.e., a system that can exchange phase (e.g. in elastic collisions) and/or energy (e.g. in inelastic collisions) with its environment.</rdfs:comment>
